Neeeeelu D - D for debt
Mujhe campus mai sabse zyada pareshan tune hi kiya hoga. Lame mom jokes, not forwarding my mail(Parth ki karta tha tu), not paying my debt. I had no idea ki galaxy ke breaks mai itni shanti se padhne wala banda kabhi itna khatarnaak ho jayega. But bhai I respect you a lot, 
you've excelled in everything you attempted, be it dance, CoD, Acads(not DS though hue hue), your research field, ya phir chikai.
Wow react karna band karde warna teri thesis defence mai aake pareshan karunga.
Tera rant pyaar ka punchnama wale rant se bohot better tha.
Quickie in the classroom, quickie in the lab...you know the rest huhu.

Inter IIT'19, Roorkee, Hall5 terrace bonfire, Secy interviews xD, Summer workshop, bazooka, Banaras, both the club treats (you left early in the first one :|), Diwali Celebration, Inter IIT'20 photo walks (missed Bombay ðŸ˜”), and bitching sessions of you know who. Club shoot baaki reh gaya, but will meet soon.
